data.description: **IT''S A LIFESTYLE** THIS STUNNING BLOCK BUILT 4-BEDROOM + DEN HOME SITS ON OVER 10,000 SQ FT OF LANDSCAPED BEAUTY! INTERIOR FEATURES INCLUDE BRAZILIAN CHERRY WOOD & 18 INCH SILVER TRAVERTINE TILED FLOORS ($30K+), RAISED PANEL OAK CABINETRY W/STAINLESS PULLS, BLACK & STAINLESS APPLIANCES, GRANITE TILE C/TOPS, BREAKFAST BAR W/PENDANT LIGHTING, CEILING FANS, VAULTED CEILINGS, WATER SOFTENER & R/O SYSTEM, BUILT-IN DESK STATION, FOCAL POINT 2-WAY FIREPLACE, WET BAR, REMODELED BATHROOMS ALL W/UPGRADED TOILETS, 6-PANEL INTERIOR DOORS, TWO-TONE PAINT SCHEME, SLATE TILED CORNER TUB IN MASTER BATH, HIS & HERS CLOSETS AND SINK STATIONS AND SO MUCH MORE. OUTSIDE YOU''LL FIND OVERSIZED PATIO SPACE, SPARKLING SWIMMING POOL, SPA W/GAZEBO, BENCH SEATING, LANDSCAPE LIGHTING & FRONT COURTYARD.
data.whatILove: Updated and ready to move-in with wood floors, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, pool, hot tub, master bedroom downstairs, front patio, large covered back patio, 2 car garage, walk-in closets, office with french double doors off entry.
